## Configuration Checklist
- [ ] Enable web search if live data beyond X is needed
- [ ] Use Grok Studio for code or document canvas work
- [ ] For large context tasks: paste documents directly — no need to summarize for context management
- [ ] For X/social research: specify the time window and signal types clearly
- [ ] API users: set system prompt for role and behavioral constraints
